{"tid":993076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山校園欺凌　男生遭扭耳鼻脫褲打屁股","createTime":"2019-01-23T15:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T10:46:51.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4dbc75d04878e46995b2b301b8a9a67978aec954","tid":993076,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山一中學今(23日)發生欺凌事件，一名男學生被約6名學生用3張椅子困在椅下，動彈不得，有幾名男學生輪流扭他的耳朵、鼻子，被欺凌者不停轉臉想避開，惟隨後又有學生脫下事主的褲子打他的屁股。<br />\n<br />\n該校校友阿恒(化名)今進入學校，在中六班房眼見該批學生正在欺凌一名男生，起初只見該男生被困在椅子下方，有人坐在椅子上，令其動彈不得，施虐者一邊笑，一邊欺凌，隨後有人脫下他的褲子打屁股，該男生說粗口要求停止施虐。阿恒稱，當時班上另有十多名學生袖手旁觀，未有人出言阻止。<br />\n<br />\n阿恒指，該校有一群學生自高中起已經常隨機欺凌他人，目標由低年級生至同級生都有，相信目的只為尋開心和貪玩，他認為校方和教師有縱容之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190123/bkn-20190123223754782-0123_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190123%2Fbkn-20190123223754782-0123_00822_001.html&d=SNcgiO0Jsq9L6NEwCudGKVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=4239953f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190123/bkn-20190123223754782-0123_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190123/photo/bkn-20190123223754782-0123_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190123232438\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190123%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190123223754782-0123_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190123232438&h=e0ce3c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190123/photo/bkn-20190123223754782-0123_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190123232438\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190123%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190123223754782-0123_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190123232438&h=b8d09515&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"387b51a83ef7a0b361dbfd69594d48a5860b3440","tid":993076,"uid":117276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:49:56.000Z","msg":"阿雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" cl